KEISLER, ACTING ATT'Y GEN.
v.
HONG Y. GAO

No. 06-1264

Supreme Court of United States.

October 1, 2007.

The petition for a writ of certiorari is granted. The judgment is vacated and the case is remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit for further consideration in light of Gonzales v. Thomas, 547 U.S. 183 (2006).
